#define cavium_dump ( str_,
buf_,
len_   ) 

Value:

{ \
   Uint32 i=0; \
   cavium_print("%s\n",str_); \
        cavium_print("0x%04X : ", i*8); \
   for (i=0;i<(Uint32)(len_);i++){    \
      if(i && ((i%8) == 0)) \
                        { \
         cavium_print( "%s", "\n"); \
                        cavium_print("0x%04X : ", (i)); \
                        } \
      cavium_print("%02x ",(buf_)[i]);\
                     } \
   cavium_print("\n%s\n",str_); \
}
